snippet.title: Dark Alliance – Emergent Combat | Dev Diary
snippet.description:
In this Dark Alliance behind-the-scenes video, Tuque Games picks a fight! Learn about the developers' quest to create the most intuitive combat experience among action RPGs, and the challenges of making every battle feel like life and death.

Preorder Dark Alliance Now - DarkAlliance.com.
Available Everywhere June 22.
